lom:description.lom:string: This site from USGS Woods Hole provides animated visualizations of coastal circulation models of the northeast coast of the United States. Data are outputs from a variety of simulation models. The site provides links to: circulation movies, software tools, and other resources.

lom:title.lom:string: Coastal Ocean Modeling at the USGS Woods Hole Science Center
